predicted%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-to-know-before-changing-your-name-legally-2018-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eunderstood%20the%20full%20impact%20of%20what%20it%20would%20mean%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20become%20Jennifer%20Lopez.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228a62c399-9401-4cb1-8dd7-524288642053%5C%22%3EPeople%20tried%20to%20call%20me%20JLo%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EInitially%2C%20it%20was%20the%20nickname%20that%20bothered%20me%20the%20most.%20At%20work%2C%20my%20colleagues%20would%20try%20to%20call%20me%20JLo%2C%20and%20I'd%20knock%20that%20down%20immediately.%20Nope%2C%20no%20way%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnickname-vs-real-name-identity-struggle-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EI%20didn't%20want%20that%20nickname%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeyond%20the%20annoying%20nickname%2C%20it%20quickly%20became%20a%20%26quot%3Bthing%26quot%3B%20that%20no%20matter%20where%20I%20was%20or%20what%20I%20was%20doing%2C%20when%20someone%20learned%20my%20name%2C%20they%20would%20make%20a%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20gets%20even%20more%20out%20of%20hand%20when%20I'm%20traveling%20in%20countries%20where%20Lopez%20is%20not%20a%20common%20surname.%20Like%20the%20time%20I%20was%20waiting%20in%20line%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffirst-safari-surprising-things-wish-i-knew-south-africa-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ein%20South%20Africa%20for%20the%20boat%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20takes%20you%20to%20tour%20Robben%20Island%2C%20and%20one%20of%20the%20guides%20taking%20tickets%20noticed%20my%20name%20and%20proceeded%20to%20tell%20everyone%20that%20Jennifer%20Lopez%20was%20getting%20on%20the%20boat%20with%20them.%20He%20even%20asked%20to%20take%20a%20photo%20with%20me.%20Or%20when%20we%20were%20taking%20the%20train%20from%20Vancouver%2C%20BC%2C%20to%20Seattle%2C%20and%20the%20border%20patrol%20decided%20to%20tell%20everyone%20on%20the%20train%20that%20there