ttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fscott-bessent-trump-tariffs-trade-negotiations-good-faith-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ETreasury%20Secretary%20Scott%20Bessent%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20on%20TV%20that%20they%20expect%20to%20raise%20%24600%20billion%20a%20year%20with%20this%20invisible%20tax%20increase.%20That's%20%2450%20billion%20a%20month%20from%20us%20and%20from%20other%20companies%20like%20us%2C%20and%20ultimately%2C%20from%20US%20consumers.%20Time%20is%20of%20the%20essence%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2237632057-8e33-40bb-ba6f-41a075a34460%5C%22%3E'It's%20tariffs%20all%20the%20time'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESomebody%20said%20to%20me%20at%20our%20company%2C%20%26quot%3BIt's%20tariffs%20all%20the%20time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20months%2C%20we%20have%20dozens%20of%20people%20working%20full-time%20or%20part-time%20on%20addressing%20all%20aspects%20of%20the%20tariffs.%20You%20can%20hardly%20imagine%20anything%20more%20disruptive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbusinesses-cost-moving-supply-chains-out-china-trump-tariff%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esupply%20chain%3C%2Fa%3E%20coming%20into%20the%20year%20was%20about%2060%25%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-and-china-reach-trade-framework-after-talks-in-london-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EChina%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20we%20also%20source%20in%20Vietnam%2C%20India%2C%20Korea%2C%20Taiwan%2C%20and%20Thailand.%20We%20make%20some%20things%20in%20the%20US%2C%20and%20we%20do%20assembly%20in%20the%20US.%20We%20also%20develop%20our%20products%20in%20the%20US%2C%20where%20we%20own%20the%20intellectual%20property.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20outsource%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcompanies-are-struggling-to-fill-existing-manufacturing-positions-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emanufacturing%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20devote%20the%20capital%20that%20we%20have%20to%20developing%20factories%2