siness%20is%20located%20north%20of%20O'Hare%20Airport%20in%20the%20Chicago%20area.%20We're%20in%20Vernon%20Hills%2C%20and%20we%20were%20going%20to%20reorganize%20some%20of%20our%20office%20and%20warehouse%20space%20and%20consolidate%20some%20of%20our%20buildings%20into%20this%20brand%20new%20building%20for%20greater%20efficiency%20and%20to%20hold%20more%20inventory.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20building%20does%20not%20exist%20%E2%80%94%20we%20were%20going%20to%20develop%20it.%20It%20was%20going%20to%20be%20not%20only%20a%20major%20investment%20by%20our%20business%2C%20but%20it%20was%20going%20to%20involve%20a%20very%20large%20investment%20in%20technology%20because%20we%20run%20a%20very%20high-tech%20fulfillment%20operation.%20It%20would%20create%20jobs%20here%20in%20Vernon%20Hills%2C%20and%20it%20would%20help%20us%20extend%20the%20life%20of%20our%20investment%20three%20more%20decades%20at%20least.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20contrary%20of%20what%20the%20government%20says%20they're%20trying%20to%20achieve.%20They're%20trying%20to%20get%20people%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdonald-trump-apple-tim-cook-india-qatar-china-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Einvest%20more%20in%20this%20country%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20this%20a%20pretty%20big%20investment%20that%20they%20completely%20screwed%20up.%20Maybe%20someday%20we'll%20be%20able%20to%20do%20it%20again%2C%20but%20right%20now%20the%20project%20is%20dead.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20top%20of%20that%2C%20we%20have%20essentially%20a%20soft%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-trump-tariff-uncertainty-affecting-businesses-spending-prices-hiring-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehiring%20freeze%3C%2Fa%3E.%20On%20April%202%2C%20I%20also%20killed%20a%20joint%20venture%20in%20India%20because%20we%20were%20just%20too%20strained%20by%20the%20tariffs.%20We've%20sharply%20cut%20our%20out-of-pocket%20expenditures%20in%20all%20parts%20of%20the%20business.%20We're%20cling